[/font][/size][/color][font=Verdana][size=4]   [color=#6fa8dc]This mod is lore-friendly and can be used as a player-home for begginers or someone who starts a new playthrough but doesn't want those fancy houses!
   Inside the house you will find a bunch of containers to put your stuff in.
